{"tid":1956454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蕭若元父子被追債　肇輝臺一帶被貼大字報","createTime":"2020-04-03T07:41:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T10:23:47.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a0ce337b2094e01f7b93ab0da4e6488f562b61c0","tid":1956454,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T07:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200403/photo/bkn-20200403083119815-0403_00822_001_01p.jpg?20200403110832\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200403%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200403083119815-0403_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20200403110832&h=9994aebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電箱被貼多張大字報。(李國健攝)<br />\n<br />\n揚言移居台灣的網台負責人蕭若元的兒子蕭定一，今日凌晨(3日)4時許，在灣仔司徒拔道近肇輝臺及皇后大道東一帶多處被貼上大字報追債，大字報上寫有「蕭若元，子債父還」等字句，並印有蕭若元的相片；大字報約數十張，分別貼於行人路欄杆、電箱及小巴站等位置。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大字報內容為「蕭若元子債父還」，並印有蕭若元的相片。(李國健攝)<br />\n<br />\n蕭若元兒子蕭定一疑因欠債，在灣仔區多處被貼大字報。<br />\n蕭若元兒子蕭定一疑因欠債，在灣仔區多處被貼大字報。"},{"pid":"a194bc60b83e008e7c772c0bb06dde72d86b3b18","tid":1956454,"uid":235875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T07:42:32.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"b96404f8087cf42bdfc75d44d3f8e571240312ab","tid":1956454,"uid":99642,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T07:43:22.000Z","msg":"父債子還<br />\n子債父還<br />\n<br />\n中國人logic goodest"},{"pid":"6ae028b0cc45f5113eea3f5507f5af72a1b750aa","tid":1956454,"uid":198258,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T07:49:31.000Z","msg":"好似話蕭定一係藍？"},{"pid":"edc86884c73b8147dbfb01df2a4eb8b8adf3e38f","tid":1956454,"uid":31637,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T07:55:24.000Z","msg":"達d燒山會唔會變成共黨傀儡？"},{"pid":"bc069230da0ad7809ed0234238adcbec2b7cc53b","tid":1956454,"uid":100772,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T07:56:25.000Z","msg":"佢話係就係咩 貼埋習大大叫佢還錢都得啦"},{"pid":"aa6c2fae50bd447b58796d969ef296dd3bb95d6a","tid":1956454,"uid":55458